Type of Feat: Class
Specifics: When you are wearing light armor, lessen the armor check penalty by 2 and increase the armor bonus by 1. This is done as a +skill bonus to (Hide, Move Silently, and Tumble) and a +2 Dodge AC bonus. This improves to +3 skills and +2 AC at 14th level and +4 skills and +3 AC at 24th level.
Use: Automatic.